It accepts both string and nested JSON, e.g. following synatx also works:
POST _security/role/click_role
{
  "indices": [
    {
      "names": [
        "events-*"
      ],
      "privileges": [
        "read"
      ],
      "query": {
        "match": {
          "category": "click"
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
The second example of this page shows an example of using nested JSON format as well.
